2.00	Lillian_Berlin	Lillian Berlin	Lillian Berlin (born Jason Berliner) is the lead singer/guitarist for St. Louis rock band Living Things. In addition Berlin is songwriter/producer and composer. He is also published author for the controversial book "Post Mortem Bliss'" and scored The Runaways film starring Kristen Stewart and Dakota Fanning. Berlin is married to acclaimed director/artist Floria Sigismondi.	
